// InputControls
// Chat message input with send and clear buttons, auto-resizing textarea, and keyboard submit.

FUNCTION handleSend()
  Trims the current input value.
  IF non-empty, calls onSend with the text and clears the input.

---

FUNCTION handleKeyDown(e)
  IF Enter is pressed without Shift, calls handleSend and prevents newline insertion.

---

FUNCTION handleInputChange(e)
  Updates the input value state.
  Adjusts the textarea height to fit content (auto-resize).

---

FUNCTION handleClear()
  Calls onClear to clear the message history.

---

FUNCTION InputControls(props) -> ReactNode                                EXPORT
  Renders an auto-resizing textarea and a row of action buttons (Send, Clear).
  Calls handleKeyDown on keypress for keyboard submit.
